---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy – Stop Sueing Valve" description="Privacy policy for Stop Sueing Valve. We do not track you beyond strictly necessary means and do not sell your data.">
	<article class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
		<header class="mb-12 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-4">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-stone-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				We respect your privacy. This policy explains what we do and do not do with your data when you use this website.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-stone-600 space-y-6 text-left">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">What we collect</h2>
				<p>
					We do not run sign-up forms, analytics trackers, or advertising on this site. We do not collect your name, email, or other personal data through the website unless you choose to email us at contact@stopsueingvalve.com. If you email us, we will use your message and contact details only to respond; we do not sell or share them with third parties for marketing.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Cookies</h2>
				<p>
					We use only strictly necessary means to run the site. If we add a cookie (e.g. for language preference or a cookie banner), we will use it only for that purpose and will state so on the site. We do not use cookies for advertising or tracking.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Hosting and access</h2>
				<p>
					The site may be hosted on a third-party platform (e.g. Vercel, Netlify, or GitHub Pages). The host may collect standard server logs (e.g. IP address, browser, requested URL) for security and operation. We do not control the host’s privacy practices; refer to their privacy policy for details.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Your rights</h2>
				<p>
					You are not required to provide any personal data to use this website. If you have contacted us by email and want to know what we hold about you or want it deleted, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@stopsueingvalve.com" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline">contact@stopsueingvalve.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Changes</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The current version will always be on this page. Last updated: January 2025.
				</p>
			</section>

			<p class="text-sm text-stone-500 pt-4 text-center">
				Contact: <a href="mailto:contact@stopsueingvalve.com" class="text-stone-700 underline hover:no-underline">contact@stopsueingvalve.com</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>
